Que raio vou vestir?

791
01:16:14,320 --> 01:16:16,230
Tu ficas aí.

792
01:16:27,960 --> 01:16:28,990
Larry.

793
01:16:30,790 --> 01:16:33,170
Larry, anda cá.

794
01:16:39,640 --> 01:16:41,180
Ed!

795
01:16:49,600 --> 01:16:51,510
Ed!

796
01:17:05,790 --> 01:17:07,740
Larry!

797
